istence across\nlayers. We also discuss some computational issues that the popular \"Louvain\"\nheuristic faces with temporal multilayer networks and suggest ways to mitigate\nthem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Dec 2014 22:52:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 14 Feb 2015 18:55:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 24 Dec 2017 18:33:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
